Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:18.75,Main,Cell,0000,0000,0000,,Deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:51.07,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:59.41,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, you aren't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:04.88,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:08.68,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miyamura-senpai. What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:10.39,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,"Wh-What"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:11.42,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:13.68,bw,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan is sleeping right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:16.18,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Can you be quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:19.35,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see him! I have something important to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:20.93,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see Hirono-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:23.40,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It will no longer reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:26.23,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:28.94,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm always by Onii-chan's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:31.75,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.65,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.86,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.22,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's in the obento today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:42.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:55.09,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious. I always look forward to your obento.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:57.23,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,How many points does it get today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:00.99,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's so delicious that it can't be scored with points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.13,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:06.56,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me how to cook next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:07.98,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:11.82,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,My sister is practicing her cooking right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:14.61,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to cook something too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:18.74,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Let's try something simple then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:19.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:30.37,Main,Cell,0000,0000,0000,,The number you have dialed is outside your calling area, or the phone might be switched off...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:33.84,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.91,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did the doctor say?
