Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.82,0:04:46.55,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(352,5,352,-55,4300,4800)}She most likely means to say "naisoku sokufuku jintai sonshou 【内側側副靭帯損傷】 which means "Medical Collateral Ligament Injury."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:43.34,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... naisoku sokusoku... jintai sokusoku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.13,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing but "soku."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.39,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of sounds like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.27,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,At least remember the name of your own injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:53.96,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to rest and not move it until it doesn't hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:57.75,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then you can't play basketball for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:58.19,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:02.90,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:04.32,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.51,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,How's your tendonitis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:10.66,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Same as usual. If I rest my arm, it will get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:14.46,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should slow down my pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.74,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.29,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Since you have to rest your knee too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Should I keep you company for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.25,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.52,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.52,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Chigiri," which means "Vow."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:40.10,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl began to look at the painting a lot."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:44.91,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"When she stared at the boy in the painting, she had a strange feeling."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:49.36,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"'Let's marry.' She somehow had that idea."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:54.74,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"In the books, there were an unusual number of stories relating to marriage."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:58.98,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"It was described as something important in people's lives."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:04.88,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She began to study the marriage system in detail."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.38,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.38,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Inori," which means "Prayer."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:10.07,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun, have you decided about your career?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:13.13,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You got a career interest survey, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.13,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's hard to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:19.23,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You should become a novelist too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:22.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to write stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.72,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I do yearn to become a novelist, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.90,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:34.70,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,After reading what you wrote, I don't think I can catch up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:37.46,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the talent after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.54,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:45.72,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with talent or anything. What's important is doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:48.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:54.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I'm about to finish writing a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:57.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I thought I couldn't possibly do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.44,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:03.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though my memory only lasts thirteen hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:06.43,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though my life experiences haven't progressed since I was twelve...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:09.95,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me that there are things I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:13.91,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, please don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:17.25,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a dream, please don't give it up, and try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:20.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.59,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.01,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.25,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:35.26,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This here has to be more like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.85,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:50.36,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird. What am I depressed about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.11,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Things are back to how they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:56.27,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I can still go wherever I want freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:08:01.41,MainF,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a place you should come or return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.32,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:10.05,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you trap yourself in the ruins of the past, nothing good will come of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:16.21,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:18.31,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You know about warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:24.60,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you remember the feeling of tenderness, you won't choose the wrong path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:29.18,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have such a faraway memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:32.28,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you already remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.94,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been better if we hadn't met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:40.01,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't remember warmth then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.42,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.42,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Surechigai," which means "Passing each other."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.85,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro's condition has improved?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:54.08,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Even though it's little by little, her memory is better than before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.41,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.01,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.67,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a different story if a miracle happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:02.02,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But miracles don't exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:07.49,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,There are only inevitabilities and accidents, and what someone has done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:08.47,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:13.10,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.66,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it. It may be too late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.46,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,The number you have dialed is outside your calling area...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.97,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.39,Main,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono Hiro-kun of grade 2 class D,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:34.22,Main,PA,0000,0000,0000,,and Miyamura Miyako-san of grade 2 class A,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:37.38,Main,PA,0000,0000,0000,,please come to the career guidance room after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.68,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What did they say, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.93,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,They asked me what I planned to do with my career interest survey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.28,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamura-senpai too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She skipped school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:53.73,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Isn't studying better than working after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:57.26,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Maybe I should take this opportunity to rehabilitate too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:01.81,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Let's go somewhere and have fun after this deadline. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.04,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Shindou Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:11.85,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Well, I'll make it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,A one-shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:19.72,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you a plot outline this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.73,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:25.99,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:28.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,They asked me to draw a one-shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:30.15,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Something other than the series.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.13,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.93,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:35.67,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,No way. You said you were going to rest just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:37.90,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I decline, there won't be a next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:44.03,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If a newcomer likes me doesn't seize every chance that passes by, he won't succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.91,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then do whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.13,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:50.95,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Club activities. If I don't move, my body will become dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:53.42,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. You were told to rest, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:56.30,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for you. You're not going to rest, even though your arm won't get better, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:59.55,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you really damage your knee, you won't be able to play basketball anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.93,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for you. If you get really hurt, you won't be able to draw manga anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:06.43,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I stop drawing, some other artist will seize the opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.68,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for me, I have to fight to be a regular!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:11.31,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you won't be able to be a regular with that injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:14.56,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:30.12,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Did I fall asleep just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.62,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,How many hours have passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.71,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,How long have I slept?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:38.48,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Only around five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.38,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I... see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.60,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you exhausted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.50,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I'm not tired at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.60,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Really? It's all right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.68,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.49,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,He really is an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:00.47,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking on more work, even though he doesn't have enough days in attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:01.82,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.65,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You can't demand planning from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.49,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you start playing basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:09.49,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I liked it from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:14.93,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It feels really good to attack swiftly, shake off your opponents, then shoot the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.27,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:16.63,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:23.12,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you capture a video that moves people's hearts from time and space gives you the best feeling there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:24.51,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.26,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for Hirono.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:30.57,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,He's way ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:34.31,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's a lot harder for him than for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.83,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,But he's an idiot after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.29,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You two are really clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:41.49,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:44.37,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... nah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.32,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfair not to finish your sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:50.27,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,When you film the life of a wild animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:54.58,Main,Cell,0000,0000,0000,,the film unit must not interfere with the behavior of that animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:58.04,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You have to shoot wildlife just as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.09,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,How does that relate to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.21,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,If I cut into the conversation between the two of you, I would be interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:06.73,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare people to animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:11.56,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. Please don't talk like you know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.65,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:17.35,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,If I look through the finder, I can see everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:14.62,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.80,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro. Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:19.57,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:22.12,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was just thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.48,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of the meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.54,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:31.34,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,11:50. I arrived at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun came four minutes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.39,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,We had lunch in the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:41.95,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The menu of the obento consisted of fried white fish, Japanese-style salad, and other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:45.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Dessert was strawberry jelly. It was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:48.51,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I always look forward to Renji-kun's obento.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.69,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"How many points does it get today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:54.07,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"It's so delicious that it can't be scored with points."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:59.01,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Please teach me how to cook next time."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:02.33,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, let's try something simple then."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:10.51,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's only three o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:16.71,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I can still remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:22.35,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.69,bw,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're still sorting your memories this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:29.31,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Before going to sleep, didn't you read over the necessary parts again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.55,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just the summaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:32.32,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Summaries?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:35.67,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I only wrote summaries into the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:39.45,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote the fun moments as fun moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:47.04,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,However, why they were fun, and how I felt, I couldn't write any of that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.17,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're thinking back about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.76,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I skim through this, I'll be able to remember in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:56.80,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll be able to remember things for longer than thirteen hours from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:16:02.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I meet Renji-kun at noon, I'll be able to remember everything until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.09,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It will take you till morning to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:05.79,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.03,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:10.15,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I don't want to lose my time with Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:13.99,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a normal girl too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.09,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:18.63,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:23.14,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.68,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless, even if you do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:26.14,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's not useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:27.64,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can keep doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.73,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:30.21,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not forcing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.84,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me. It's bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:37.01,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please give it back to me. Give it back. I beg you, please give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:41.14,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Inside that... inside that, is my Renji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.60,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.36,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:55.78,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.33,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for saying something selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.16,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.67,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.67,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Genzai," which means "Present."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,How was it when we first met?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:20.30,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to retain the important past in my heart one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.51,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:24.97,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:30.11,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You kept gazing at the sky. It gave me a strange feeling somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.44,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sky, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:35.91,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was indeed looking at the sky at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:41.28,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But now it's more fun to look in front of me than at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.29,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:49.12,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.58,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:57.26,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, if it's okay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.84,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can we hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:05.89,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.94,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want to force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.14,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking of trying to hold hands for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.89,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can... we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:19.78,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:23.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.35,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.42,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:43.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro! Chihiro! Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.89,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.89,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Kurayami," which means "Darkness."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:48.42,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl married on the next day."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:51.39,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She found a dress in the castle."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:57.81,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She pretended to ask herself, 'Do you vow to marry?' in her mind, and she pretended to answer 'Yes.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:19:02.19,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"And then she kissed the boy in the painting."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:03.90,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"It tasted like oil."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:08.40,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She threw the flowers that she picked as a bouquet."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:11.33,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"She prepared a bigger meal than usual."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:13.52,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"It was a party after all."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:19.08,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"But she had leftovers, because the dress was too tight around the hips."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:27.17,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl tossed the bouquet, the dress, and the leftovers to the bottom of the dump site and went to sleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.50,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"And thus the wedding ceremony was over."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.38,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:37.16,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:37.60,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.82,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.73,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:44.74,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Is Chihiro all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:49.32,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Strain and lack of sleep, plus mental stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:54.00,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She kept straining herself, so she broke down once she felt relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:58.37,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to wake her up several times, but it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:02.30,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She passed her time limit already, so just let her sleep quietly for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.05,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Time limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:06.80,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:14.22,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-san, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.85,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.19,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:28.32,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why have I grown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:30.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to my eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.57,0:20:31.57,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:34.41,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Onee-chan? Where's Kei-onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:37.88,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hiro-onii-chan? What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:37.88,Main2,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.21,Main2,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You already...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:41.46,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.96,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:44.88,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:49.10,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.08,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, do you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.36,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Himura... onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.36,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You still remember me, don't you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.28,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Now you understand, right? This is Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:20.80,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is stuck at twelve years old and thirteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:22.50,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:03.56,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Hirono.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.10,0:23:05.91,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.29,0:23:10.99,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:14.86,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.68,0:23:16.83,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:17.83,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:21.57,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What, so you do remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:25.30,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? I was worried because I couldn't get in touch with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:27.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on your phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:29.47,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,So I didn't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:34.49,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't disappeared yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:39.39,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't know about pain, you will face a more painful tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:43.33,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, ef - a tale of memories:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:44.73,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Forget me not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:48.26,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have memories you don't want to forget?
